[b]Step 2:[/b]
Open your ItemPacketHandler class, and add this to your imports:
[/size][/font][code]import com.rs2.model.content.skills.CuttingGems;[/code][font=tahoma][size=13px]


Next, search for this:
[/size][/font][code]Item useWithItem = player.getInventory().getItemContainer().get(withSlot);[/code][font=tahoma][size=13px]

Below, add this:
[/size][/font][code]CuttingGems.handleChisel(useItem, useWithItem, player);[/code][font=tahoma][size=13px]

That`s it.

